<div id="readme">
<h2>Drive Smash Burn</h2>
<ul>

<li><strong>High Concept:</strong>
To smash all of the sports cars in the dealership
</li>

<li><strong>Player Experience Goals:</strong>
I want the player to play the game to try and get the highest score (destroy all of the cars) and then i want the player to go back and look to see if they can find the hidden room with the slegde hammer in it.
</li>

<li><strong>Genre:</strong>
The genre for the game is a top-down action game.
</li>

<li><strong>Game play:</strong>
Aroow keys to move your player. Q swings your weapon when you are PUSHING against a car. 
Your mission is to go into the dealership and destory all of the cars. Then leave before you are caught. **Avoid the lazer alarms or else the cops will show up in 20 seconds and arrest you**
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype goal:</strong>
My prototype goal was to work with entering different places in one level, which introduces the ability for hidden areas and loot. I also wanted to try to include multiple endings in the game.
</li>

<li><strong>Features:</strong>
This game features the basic aviod objects and attack other objects events. Another feature is a secret room hidden in the game where you can pick up a slegde hammer instead of a baseball bat to smash the cars evern faster.
</li>

<li><strong>Setting/Premise:</strong>
The setting is outside of a car dealership and inside the car dealership.
</li>

<li><strong>Story:</strong>
You are an agent for hire. A foriegn car company has hired you to destroy the competition. This job is very important to you, for if you fail this job there wont be another one.
</li>

<li><strong>Target Audience:</strong>
The target audience is the people that are tired of trying to drive the sports car and want to see some destruction.
</li>

<li><strong>Play time:</strong>
3-6 minutes
</li>

<li><strong>Strategies:</strong>
Find the hidden weapon to destory the cars faster!!!!!
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Assets:</strong>
I created all of my assets
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Closest Other Game:</strong>

</li>

</ul>
</div>
